---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Ottawa Weekly privacy policy."
>
  <Nav />

  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <h1 class="font-display text-forest text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-8">Last updated: March 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-sm">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What we collect</h2>
        <p>
          When you subscribe to Ottawa Weekly, we collect your email address and, optionally, your first name. This information is used solely to send you the newsletter.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How we use it</h2>
        <p>
          Your email is used to send Ottawa Weekly, a free weekly newsletter. We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Email service provider</h2>
        <p>
          We use Beehiiv to manage our subscriber list and deliver the newsletter. Beehiiv's privacy policy applies to the processing of your data on their platform.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          This website uses privacy-respecting analytics (Plausible or Fathom) that do not use cookies or collect personal information. No cookie consent banner is required.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Unsubscribing</h2>
        <p>
          Every issue of Ottawa Weekly includes an unsubscribe link. You can remove yourself from the list at any time with one click. We comply with Canada's Anti-Spam Legislation (CASL).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-forest text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@ottawaweekly.ca" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-hover transition-colors duration-200">hello@ottawaweekly.ca</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
